    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129000/extras/27dc420e26853949e80e59a1ddf8232c.avif?t=1682868262\" width=500 height=128 /></span><br><br>You've been invited to a strange party at Lady Tealwoods' new mansion. The other members of the guestlist are strange and often quarrelsome, and you are all locked in until midnight. A sudden murder is revealed, and you must piece together who is lying, and who is the murderer as you uncover the secrets of the different strange guests of Tealwoods Manor.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129000/extras/7a3a32aec60639f9ba196ee7efeb9479.avif?t=1682868262\" width=500 height=128 /></span><br><br>13 playable characters with unique dialogue.<br>A murderer randomly selected from the attendee's, unique every game.<br>The murderer will cleverly lie to you, and frantic guests will claim they saw anything, up to you to figure out what the truth is.<br>Up to 20 million unique combinations of dialogue and scenarios built into the game's randomization engine.<br>wager on which guests will survive the night in an attempt to score the most points.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129000/extras/b917d3dcbb27748c3ce2a3741c2f4035.avif?t=1682868262\" width=500 height=128 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129000/extras/f1a4f45ee0a47f2f6875f8ea05850528.avif?t=1682868262\" width=500 height=350 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129000/extras/0a7dc11bfffbe43756de42d929872e99.avif?t=1682868262\" width=500 height=350 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><